---
title: multiply_polynomialcoeff (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_assert : assert len(a) + len(b) <= FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_EXT_BLOB
    q_assert --> q_init_r : r = PolynomialCoeff([0])
    q_init_r --> q_iter : for power, coef in enumerate(a)
    q_iter --> q_summand : summand = [0]*power + [coef * x for x in b]
    q_summand --> q_accumulate : r = add_polynomialcoeff(r, summand)
    q_accumulate --> q_iter : next coefficient
    q_iter --> q_return : all coefficients processed
    q_return --> [*] : return r

    note right of q_assert
        INV: Product degree <= FIELD_ELEMENTS_PER_EXT_BLOB - 1
        INV: Result degree = deg(a) + deg(b)
    end note
